{"title":"风","authors":["朱子奇"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":8,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱子奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即席书赠澳大利亚《西风》杂志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主编布鲁斯·本内特先生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边的东风把春天吹送，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边的“西风”也把春天吹送。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风呵，吹吧！吹吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫荡了那北方的严寒之冬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹来温暖和友谊乐融融。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边的东风把和平唱颂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边的“西风”也把和平唱颂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风呵，唱吧！唱吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱散了那战争的乌云重重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱出人间和星际的繁荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1981年2月15日夜于北京"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}